21#include <limits.h>
22#include "mpc-impl.h"
23
24int
25mpc_ui_div (mpc_ptr a, unsigned long int b, mpc_srcptr c, mpc_rnd_t rnd)
26{
27 int inex;
28 mpc_t bb;
29
30 mpc_init2 (bb, sizeof(unsigned long int) * CHAR_BIT);
31 mpc_set_ui (bb, b, rnd); /* exact */
32 inex = mpc_div (a, bb, c, rnd);
33 mpc_clear (bb);
34
35 return inex;
36}
